name: Men's Street Jacket
description:
One of a kind fully-lined and insulated Men's Street Jacket!

This jacket is a one-off, meaning there is only one of these made! The jacket features a full zippered closure, a vertical chest pocket, and matching side zippered pockets with snap closure flaps. The hem of the jacket is ribbed and has an interior chest pocket.

The main body of the jacked is a quilted and insulated nylon, while the sleeves are a contrast sweatshirt fleece.

Materials
Shell:
100% Nylon
100% Cotton
Lining:
100% Cotton

Measurements:
Length (HPS to Bottom of Hem): 27"
Sleeve Length: 26"
Chest Width (1" Below Armscye): 21 1/2"

name: Women's Denim Shorts
description:
Women's Denim Shorts!

The material is a very awesome bright blue, 100% cotton, mid weight denim. The pockets are a beige, 100% cotton, lightweight pocketing. The shorts feature a contrast grey topstitching with a matching grey zipper, and a black button closure at the front! There is some slight fitting aspects as well with two sets of darts, one set in the front and one set in the back.

Shell: Bright Blue 100% Cotton Denim
Pocketing: Beige 100% Cotton Pocketing
Waist Circumference: 25 1/2"
Waist to Hem Length: 18 1/2"

Just in time for Summer!
